name: snapshotTime
description: Where the data was filtered and put into the table

name: projectId
description: ProjectId of table that could not be backed up

name: datasetId
description: DatasetId of table that could not be backed up

name: tableId
description: TableId of table that could not be backed up

name: partitionId
description: PartitionId of table that could not be backed up

name: lastModifiedTime
description: LastModifiedTime of table (from GCP Census) that could not be backed up

name: backupLastModifiedTime
description: date of last modification (from GCP Census) of backup table

name: backupEntityLastModifiedTime
description: date of last modification (from Datastore Export) that will be included in the Backup (copyJob start time - as it is atomic operation and every change before that point is included in copy)

name: numBytes
description: Number of bytes of table (from GCP Census) that could not be backed up

name: backupNumBytes
description: Number of bytes of table backup (from GCP Census)

name: backupEntityNumBytes
description: Number of bytes of table backup (from Datastore)

name: numRows
description: Number of rows of table (from GCP Census) that could not be backed up

name: backupNumRows
description: Number of rows of table backup (from GCP Census)
